item.title: We Want...UCF?
item.description: We want Bama! That has been the call of underdog teams for years, ever since Nick Saban took over the Alabama Crimson Tide football team and made them into the the powerhouse they are today. Watch any episode of College Gameday from the past few years and you’re bound to see someone holding a sign claiming that the school hosting Gameday could roll with the Tide. However, this isn’t about Alabama.
